			<h3 ><a href="#p3980" rel="nofollow"><!-- google_ad_section_start -->Re: Is Trading Markakis an Option?<!-- google_ad_section_end --></a></h3>
			<p class="author"><!-- google_ad_section_start(weight=ignore) --><a rel="nofollow" href="./viewtopic.php?p=3980&amp;sid=42580cfaf169a1b5b7fc9a6b2d807995#p3980"><img src="./styles/static/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>Post <a href="./viewtopic.php?p=3980&amp;sid=42580cfaf169a1b5b7fc9a6b2d807995#p3980" onclick="prompt('Direct link to post:',this.href); return false;"><strong>#2</strong></a>&nbsp;by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2&amp;sid=42580cfaf169a1b5b7fc9a6b2d807995" style="color: #000000;" class="username-coloured">Jordan Tuwiner</a></strong> &raquo; October 3rd, 2011, 7:36 pm <!-- google_ad_section_end --></p>

			

			<div id="explanation3980" style="display:none" >
					<form action="" method="post">
						<fieldset>
							<textarea name="comment_text" cols="60" rows="5"></textarea><br />
